{% comment %}
These are the necessary variables examples to correctly initialize the component:

1. {% assign videoPoster =
        'WDLK_Brand-Video-Poster.jpg' | file_img_url %}
2. {% assign videoWebM =
        'WDLK_Brand-Video-Bg.webm' | file_url %}
3. {% assign videoMp4 =
        'WDLK_Brand-Video-Bg.mp4' | file_url %}
